title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Belgium - Museum aan de Stroom
description:
In this video we will fly over the Museum aan de Stroom . The Museum aan de Stroom (MAS; Dutch for: Museum by the Stream) is a museum located along the river Scheldt in the Eilandje district of Antwerp, Belgium. It opened in May 2011 and is the largest museum in Antwerp.
